Package: seerrng
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs (>= 22), adduser, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Standalone media request and discovery service
 SeerrNG can be configured to integrate with external Plex, Jellyfin, Emby,
 Sonarr, Radarr, Lidarr, and Readarr-compatible services. Those services are
 optional and are managed separately from this package.
